{"tid":764930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【無綫地震】傳全部部門減10%人手　前員工爆料日內派大信封","createTime":"2018-08-02T11:00:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T12:53:28.000Z","uid":5195,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"27febfa43a21bce7406bc364162de6e2befca3b9","tid":764930,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:00:07.000Z","msg":"無綫裁員潮真係未停過，早前已有指無綫近年生意額大減，所以各部門都要「交人」。（新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2KFwYC3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KFwYC3&d=PweQtpxxUf4jGkbaBIHExdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c165a133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2KFwYC3</a> ）今日《蘋果》再收到聲稱係無綫中人嘅李先生（化名）爆料，指TVB日內會再派大信封，計劃每個部門都要裁減10%人手。<br />\n<br />\n李先生稱TVBI嘅裁員已大致完成，下一波會輪到TVB，李先生話：「之前話TVBI會裁四成人手，咁原本百幾二百人，炒咗大約60-80個。今日再聽其他部門講，娛樂新聞台現在總共約有80人就裁咗5個人，on air service大約20人裁兩個，都係呢幾日會派信。咁如果你個部門本身都係唔夠人，可能有得豁免嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n李先生承認自己都係被裁人員之一，問到現在公司氣氛係咪好差？佢話：「咁梗係唔好啦，成日話裁員，大家都係等消息，有啲睇吓其他部門可唔可以調過去，或者自己諗定後路囉。一間公司幾年改一次，難保過多幾個月，話生意咁差又裁多鑊，咁市場賺少咗就要cut budget，我哋都冇辨法。」"},{"pid":"cb5096836e4336ed2837814d37866d7f9b1d1436","tid":764930,"uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"亞視化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1c79e4d8c3b3b4c4d74e20d578ed4218e6cac3","tid":764930,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"近幾年搞乜衰乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8daa9c747c5387a8032d0a9818961156bc71dc","tid":764930,"uid":693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"笑出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665f8628067a4cb05c2323d